    <div class="exp-why-grid">

      <div class="exp-why-card">
        <div class="exp-why-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>1:1 Tutoring</h4>
        <p>1:1 tutoring as standard here in Squamish. You won't spend the day waiting for your turn. Every session is built around you, your camera, and what's in front of us.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="exp-why-card">
        <div class="exp-why-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Entirely In The Field</h4>
        <p>Over ten years photographing wildlife across three continents. I teach what I actually do. Reading situations, best ethical approaches, anticipating behaviour. Not what a textbook says.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="exp-why-card">
        <div class="exp-why-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Tailored to You</h4>
        <p>No fixed workshops. Whether you've just bought your first camera or want to sharpen a specific skill, we focus entirely on what will move your photography forward.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="section-label" style="margin-top: 3rem;">Session Options</p>
    <div class="exp-format-grid">

      <div class="exp-format-card">

        <div class="exp-format-header">
