            <p class="exp-format-label">1:1</p>
            <h3 class="exp-format-title">Private Session</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="exp-format-desc">Just you and me in the field. Fully focused, entirely at your pace. I find this is most effective way to improve quickly. We'll review images together as we shoot and adjust in real time.</p>
        <ul class="exp-format-list">
          <li>2-5 hours, your choice</li>
